Package: RightOmicsTools
Title: Complementary tools to manipulate and visualize single-cell RNA-seq data
Version: 2.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Alexis", family = "Varin", email = "alexis.varin@inserm.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0001-3474-7263"))
Description: This package is a collection of various tools to facilitate the analysis of single-cell RNA-seq data in R. It is intended to be used in conjunction with other packages, such as Seurat, and is not a standalone package. The package is currently in development and will be updated regularly with new functions and improvements.
